title: Tyranid 6th edition codex
description:
In the grim darkness of the present there is only radioactive fallout from Fukushima, rising ocean temperatures, and total corporate control of our lives. We are in essence corporate serfs living on a dying planet. Thankfully we have Pirate Bay!

Dear reader, you have clicked the link to the heretical codex of the Xenos Tyranids, creatures whose origin remains a mystery, but whose intent is clear, they seek to consume all life in the galaxy. This link will provide you with the torrent to the pdf. file codex. Enjoy. I am merely uploading this, I was not the original source.
